title: Emprox 2019 Bootcamp Video

embed.description: Our League of Legends team returned to Sydney in 2019 for their annual boot camp ahead of their playoff matches in the Oceanic Challenger Series. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ► Follow us! * Twitter - https://twitter.com/emproxgg * Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/emproxgg/ * Website: http://emproxgg.com/ * Discord - https://t.co/Ous2eUyUSh -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

body:
Emprox accomplished another bootcamp in 2019 with amazing success with the team finishing the highest it has in the last 3 years of competition.

The team will be starting its recruitment process in the coming months.
There is also rumored to be a game house in store for the 2020 season for this OCS team.
